************
Introduction
************

Django-TemplateUtils is a set of tools for use with Django's templates, 
template tags and context processors.

************
Installation
************

Requirements
============

This application requires:

* Django. The application targets the most recent release of branch 1.x.

Please install and configure these applications *before* this one.

Get the code
============

The code is not published yet. Ask the author.
Copy the templateutils folder somewhere in your PYTHON_PATH. It may be in your
project's directory.

Settings
========

* add 'templateutils' to your INSTALLED_APPS

